title: Libya in Multinational $2.7 Billion Deal to Develop Misrata Zone
description: Libya signed a partnership deal that involves Qatari, Italian and Swiss companies to expand and develop the Misrata Free Zone port terminal on the Mediterranean, the OPEC member said.
